              "title": "Whiff drill",
              "description": "- set cpu to block and punish \n- record a jab or fast recovery move and a slow recovery move \n- react to the jab with a jab or df1 punish \n- react to the bigger whiff with a launch ",
              "createdAt": "2025-07-13T04:48:39.237Z",
              "labels": [],
              "checklist": []
            },
            {
              "id": "e3f44674-4f5b-4049-a6ca-7ea429eccf89",
              "title": "Advanced whiff drill",
              "description": "Situational drill to create awareness of different options to go for \n\nEx: Zafina b1+2 > BD > launch a whiff \nLaunch \n\nZafina f3 > scr2,1 heat guaranteed or f1+2 \n\n- record a specific barrage of actions that create chip damage \n- end it with a planned whiff sequence and use heat engager\n- record a similar barrage but none to little chip and launch ",
              "createdAt": "2025-07-13T05:05:17.827Z",
              "labels": [],
              "checklist": []
            },
            {
              "id": "b5f4704d-cd64-4dd0-af5b-2c54aa066952",
              "title": "Grab/reaction drill",
              "description": "- set cpu to block and punish with plus frame to command grab and a 20-22 frame low \n- do a safe move and break grabs block low \n- extra: set CPU to pressure > low > pressure > command grab OR low \n\nThis adds complexity if you miss the low to keep defending after ",
              "createdAt": "2025-07-13T04:47:03.357Z",
              "labels": [],
              "checklist": []
            },
            {
              "id": "e664706a-14ef-4b55-b777-deba79e49a7c",
              "title": "Advanced reaction drill",
              "description": "- set cpu to block and punish with 1 jab into grabs/ command grabs \n- do a minus move and mash a jab so you get ch/interrupted by the jab \n- break the throw \n- add in string or low or problem move after jab \n- ex: jab to drag db3+4 or some mid high string ",
